  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1308975/" class="title-link">“一切历史都是思想史”的提出</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1308975"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/Hristotle/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1318515-15.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Hristotle/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Theta</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-02-20"
      class="main-meta">2008-02-20 23:16:47</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1308975_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                    英国当代哲学家沃尔什在其《历史哲学导论》一书中，将近现代的历史哲学划分为思辨的历史哲学与分析的历史哲学。而柯林武德则是分析的历史哲学的代表人物，尤其柯林武德提出的“一切历史都是思想史”，对分析的历史哲学中历史解释的探究影响深远。在柯林武德之前洛克、休谟等...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1308975/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">34有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
